  <description>
    <p>In a time long ago, there lived in the kingdom of Equestria,
      a unicorn named Twilight.
      This silly yet intelligent mare loved her fellow citizens for their simple
      and peaceful ways, so she raised a programmer of joy and set out to spread
      happiness everywhere.</p>
    <p>This is her program.</p>
  </description>

